OL,5, Ford is to invest #230m in its Halewood
OL,6, plant on Merseyside to make electric   
OL,7, car parts, helping safeguard 500 jobs. 
OL,9,FThe investment will mean the plant will
OL,10,Frun for many years longer, said Stuart 
OL,11,FRowley, president, Ford of Europe.     
OL,13,FThere had been speculation about the   
OL,14,Ffuture of the Halewood factory complex 
OL,15,Fas Ford moves towards electrifying its 
OL,16,Fvehicles.                              
OL,18,FPart of the investment will come from  
OL,19,Fthe government's Automotive            
OL,20,FTransformation Fund.                   
